 1.57a3.4 3.4 0 0 1-2.47 1.02c-.97 0-1.8-.34-2.49-1.03l-1.3-1.3a3.55 3.55 0 0 1-1-2.51v-.01h-.02v.02zm5.39-3.43c0-.19.02-.4.07-.63.13-.74.44-1.37.95-1.87l.66-.67.97-.98 1.56-1.56c.68-.69 1.5-1.03 2.47-1.03.97 0 1.8.34 2.48 1.02l1.3 1.32a3.48 3.48 0 0 1 1 2.48c0 .58-.11 1.11-.37 1.6l-.02.02v.02l-.02.04c-.14.27-.35.54-.6.8L16.23 15l-.01.02-.01.02c-.44.42-.92.7-1.43.83a4.55 4.55 0 0 0 1.23-3.52L18 10.38c.18-.21.3-.42.35-.65a2.03 2.03 0 0 0-.01-.9 1.96 1.96 0 0 0-.36-.58l-1.3-1.3a1.49 1.49 0 0 0-1.06-.42c-.42 0-.77.14-1.06.4l-1.2 1.27-.8.8-1.16 1.15c-.08.08-.18.21-.29.4a1.66 1.66 0 0 0-.08 1.12l.02.03v.02l.06.14s.01.03.05.06l.06.13.02.02.01.02.01.02c.05.08.1.13.14.16l.47.5c0 .04-.02.09-.04.15l-.06.12-1.15 1.15-.1.08-.56-.56a2.3 2.3 0 0 0-.18-.19c-.02-.01-.02-.03-.02-.04l-.02-.02a.37.37 0 0 1-.1-.12c-.03-.03-.05-.04-.05-.06l-.1-.15-.02-.02-.02-.04-.08-.17v-.02a5.1 5.1 0 0 1-.28-.69 1.03 1.03 0 0 1-.04-.26c-.06-.23-.1-.46-.1-.7v.01z" fill="#A8A8A8"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><div class="bl l"><div><div class="bk" aria-hidden="false"></div></div></div></div></header><span class="l"></span><section><div><div class="ds gw gx gy gz ha"></div><div class="hb hc hd he hf"><div class=""><h1 id="ea05" class="pw-post-title hg hh hi bd hj hk hl hm hn ho hp hq hr hs ht hu hv hw hx hy hz ia ib ic id ie bi">Star Atlas Pirate Guild “The Unseen” is Recruiting</h1></div><p id="8b8a" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc hb bi">The Unseen is a Pirates Guild with a focus solely on Star Atlas. <strong class="ih hj">No Mercy, No Surrender!</strong></p><p id="5609" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc hb bi"><strong class="ih hj">So you think you are a Pirate?</strong></p><figure class="jd je jf jg fd jh"><div class="bz dy l di"><div class="ji jj l"></div></div></figure><h2 id="02b6" class="jk jl hi bd jm jn jo jp jq jr js jt ju iq jv jw jx iu jy jz ka iy kb kc kd ke bi"><strong class="ak">Why choose The Unseen?</strong></h2><p id="11c0" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii kf ik il im kg io ip iq kh is it iu ki iw ix iy kj ja jb jc hb bi">The Unseen is a Pirates Guild with a focus solely on Star Atlas. A number of other guilds tend to dabble in several different metaverses, but with us, you will only be focused on growing and profiting in Star Atlas. Finalist in the 1st Annual Joni Awards for Best Small Guild and Best Guild Website!</p><p id="593e" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc hb bi">We are also the hosts of the Community Initiative project “<strong class="ih hj">The Unseen’s Dog Fighting Championship</strong>” more information can be found at <a class="ae kk" href="https://unseenguild.com/dfc" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">https://unseenguild.com/dfc</a>. The Unseen offers an exclusive Ranks and Rewards system that will grant members NFTs for promotions and achievements! All information on this can be found on our website.</p><h2 id="4ace" class="jk jl hi bd jm jn jo jp jq jr js jt ju iq jv jw jx iu jy jz ka iy kb kc kd ke bi"><strong class="ak">What we are looking for</strong></h2><p id="29d0" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii kf ik il im kg io ip iq kh is it iu ki iw ix iy kj ja jb jc hb bi">We are looking for members that want to be aggressive, active, and loyal to the crew. Some others look down upon the aggressive nature of a game of this sort, we thrive on it. We will live on combat, and we are looking for <strong class="ih hj">Gamers</strong> and <strong class="ih hj">Pirates</strong>! More information on specifics can be had by reaching out to The Unseen leadership team.</p><h2 id="80b1" class="jk jl hi bd jm jn jo jp jq jr js jt ju iq jv jw jx iu jy jz ka iy kb kc kd ke bi"><strong class="ak">Leadership History</strong></h2><p id="0ab8" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii kf ik il im kg io ip iq kh is it iu ki iw ix iy kj ja jb jc hb bi">The Unseen is run by twin brothers that have combined MMO, Shooter, and Action-Adventure leadership experience of over 30 years. We have run guilds, clans, companies, and squads in a multitude of games and have always been on the competitive edge. We also have a large number of leadership positions in all our branches that remain unfilled.</p><h2 id="4713" class="jk jl hi bd jm jn jo jp jq jr js jt ju iq jv jw jx iu jy jz ka iy kb kc kd ke bi">Faction: <strong class="ak">MUD</strong></h2><h2 id="7440" class="jk jl hi bd jm jn jo jp jq jr js jt ju iq jv jw jx iu jy jz ka iy kb kc kd ke bi">Activities:</h2><p id="d4d5" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii kf ik il im kg io ip iq kh is it iu ki iw ix iy kj ja jb jc hb bi"><strong class="ih hj">Piracy</strong>, Industry, Material Management, Bounty Hunting, Escort Services, Trade, Land Management, Mercenary Work</p><p id="7977" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc hb bi"><strong class="ih hj">Language: English Only</strong></p><h1 id="73f0" class="kl jl hi bd jm km kn ko jq kp kq kr ju ks kt ku jx kv kw kx ka ky kz la kd lb bi">Contact The Unseen and Join Today</h1><p id="dee8" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii kf ik il im kg io ip iq kh is it iu ki iw ix iy kj ja jb jc hb bi"><strong class="ih hj">Website:</strong> <a class="ae kk" href="https://unseenguild.com/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">https://unseenguild.com/</a></p><p id="4648" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc hb bi"><strong class="ih hj">Discord:</strong> <a class="ae kk" href="https://discord.gg/YKmXzjWkp7" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">https://discord.gg/YKmXzjWkp7</a></p><p id="c4ed" class="pw-post-body-paragraph if ig hi ih b ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc hb bi"><strong class="ih hj">Twitter:</strong> <a class="ae kk" href="https://twitter.com/TheUnseenGuild" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/TheUnseenGuild</a></p><figure class="jd je jf jg fd jh er es paragraph-image"><div class="er es lc"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1216/format:webp/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 1216w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 608px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1216/1*7iybJo1i6uh7MfRD27_M7g.png